revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
{{High-use}}
<!-- EDIT TEMPLATE DOCUMENTATION BELOW THIS LINE -->
'''Sub'''scripts text, i.e.
: <code><nowiki>{{sub|Text to be subscripted}}</nowiki></code> produces: {{sub|Text to be subscripted}}

This template may be listed at [[Wikipedia:Subst]] as a good candidate for substituting (i.e. <nowiki>{{subst:sub}}</nowiki>). On a page that uses the template many times, however, this is likely to clutter and lengthen the page significantly.

Text can also be subscripted simply by using the <nowiki><sub> and </sub></nowiki> tags, so that:
: <code><nowiki><sub>Text to be subscripted</sub></nowiki></code>  also produces: <sub>Text to be subscripted</sub>
==Template Data==
{{template data header}}
<templatedata>
{
	"params": {
		"1": {
			"label": "subscripted text",
			"type": "line",
			"required": true
		}
	},
	"description": "subscript text",
	"format": "inline"
}
</templatedata>

== See also ==
{{Sup and sub-related templates |expanded}}
{{Math templates|notation |state=collapsed}}

<includeonly>{{Sandbox other||
<!-- ADD CATEGORIES BELOW THIS LINE -->
[[Category:Superscript and subscript templates]]
[[Category:Mathematical formatting templates]]
[[Category:Wikipedia XHTML tag-replacing templates]]
}}</includeonly>

